                    <span>As an American baby boomer, I knew little about the battle fought just after the Normandy invasion. This book describes the intensity of that fight, and touches on the Falaise Pocket.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">excellent insight vision</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
